skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cafe noir
des: A cafe that contains a list of items including food and beverages where users can request the price of each item. They can also ask alexa for the menu as well as opening time, closing time and special of the day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
